      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, but honestly, she\u2019s worth every second. It\u2019s truly rare to find one kept in such immaculate, showroom-ready shape\u2014it still feels like a dream every time you get behind the wheel. I\u2019m only letting her go because I want someone else to experience that same 'new car' magic every time they open the garage door. She's been pampered, garage-kept, and is looking for a new home where she'll be just as loved. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. Come take a look, have a chat, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this one!",
